{"tid":2296784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深井發生三屍命案　婦人和19、21歲子女疑燒炭自殺身亡","createTime":"2020-11-22T18:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T03:10:35.000Z","uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"72019219ee35f0380a7f60197b46b36be6cd20c9","tid":2296784,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"深井發生三屍命案，一名婦人和其19和21歲子女懷疑燒炭自殺身亡。據了解，婦人近日正與丈夫商討離婚安排。<br />\n<br />\n消防和救護車一度出動，現場是深井浪翠園3期10座一個單位，警方下午近一時，接獲一名男子報案指返回住所時大門反鎖，消防破門入屋，發現戶主的妻子和一對子女倒斃其中一間房內。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，屍體已發脹，現場檢獲燒過的炭，沒有遺書。據了解，男戶主與太太感情出問題、已搬走兩個月，上周三最後一次聯絡太太商討離婚安排。據了解，他的兒子19歲，女兒21歲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFhl_FDqimA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjFhl_FDqimA&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=78d0aa2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFhl_FDqimA</a>"},{"pid":"b2a853d4c637d14f07f1bcfb6d676095c9bd1b0b","tid":2296784,"uid":72228,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"19 21歲都無反抗<br />\n睇嚟似比家人落左藥<br />\n宜家咁多成家自殺咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0bd0bd5e3741af41c82a8636a7d5ca9844864f","tid":2296784,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:59:37.000Z","msg":"離婚好閒<br />\n仔女都成年人啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a7bb489c6401aba83270f33c89ede76bf0222c","tid":2296784,"uid":245484,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"19 21 都跟? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點睇都係謀殺啦下麻"},{"pid":"c20546a65d43ec8e6bfccbf4132575f064bc6f5e","tid":2296784,"uid":8014,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:26:25.000Z","msg":"19/21 啱啱接觸花花世界 鬼會同你癲陪你自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個老母正一仆街<b